The Squier maple neck is from the Affinity Series and has had a very nice headstock makeover with many coats of clear over the decal. Near zero fret wear . The bridge is a vintage ash tray style string through the body three saddle bridge. The very cool full thickness Gloss Xaviere Sunburst body is in excellent condition, just mild surface scratches. The pickups are a GFS Alnico single coils. I also upgraded the tone capacitor with a nice .033uf axial film capacitor. All electronics work perfectly,and sound great on every setting,clean or with some distortion. These pickups sound very good on this guitar. Action is good and this Tele packs a punch.
